      <title>津巴布韦拥有 3.7 亿美元储备来支持货币：邮报</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-07/zimbabwe-has-370-million-in-reserves-to-back-currency-mail</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据津巴布韦国家通讯社星期日邮报援引津巴布韦央行行长约翰·穆沙亚万胡的话报道，支持津巴布韦新货币的现金和矿产储备在过去三个月内从 2.85 亿美元增至约 3.7 亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-07/zimbabwe-has-370-million-in-reserves-to-back-currency-mail</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 07 Jul 2024 09:21:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
